{"type": "article", "id": 3930, "title": "哈苏奢华型便携相机 Stellar II", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-28T07:55:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233135zZFPa5ij6VQxGUXp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t瑞典相机生产商哈苏（Hasselblad）推出了奢华型便携相机 Stellar II 这个烧钱的玩意儿。哈苏Stellar II 是以 RX100 为基础，配合多款不同把手材质设计重新包装推出，专为摄影发烧友而设计。Stellar II 像素达 2000 万，搭载了 3.0 英寸的高分辨率屏幕、一个 3.6 倍光学变焦的索尼蔡司镜头、NFC 技术以及内置的 Wi-Fi 功能，为用户在电脑、智能手机、平板电脑等设备上共享照片提供了便利。此外，Stellar II 还可以连接闪光灯与麦克风。提供橄榄木、胡桃木、紫檀木以及碳化纤维 4 种材质的把手，定价 1650 欧元。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233133NdUA1gKnVRrexFas.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233134v2KGiLaOTo4MEmw8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233134XJrYCZDKIw9fukt4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6109375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233134zateSJjx614rqVbH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.759375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052331350vCbkNdVw194JthE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}